Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.56,0:00:32.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英\N{\rENG}The Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们相信吗\N{\rENG}Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她居然亲手将自己奉上\N{\rENG}And she just handed herself in.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错, 你们捉住我了\N{\rENG}That's right. You caught me.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}星际罪犯玫瑰石\N{\rENG}Galactic Criminal Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我爱粉碎钻石\N{\rENG}I love shattering Diamonds.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.87,0:00:44.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事就想着粉碎钻石\N{\rENG}I just want to shatter 'em all the time.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你以为粉碎你就能解决问题! \N{\rENG}You think shattering's bad?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.58,0:00:49.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等着瞧吧, 钻石们可有的是办法让你好受\N{\rENG}Wait till the Diamonds get their hands on you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}至少大家都安全了\N{\rENG}At least everyone else is safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.81,0:00:54.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你干什么! 放我走! \N{\rENG}What are you doing? Let go of me!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.45,0:00:57.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! \N{\rENG}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么…拉尔斯! \N{\rENG}What the... Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.89,0:01:03.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦! 看上去我们还是捉到了一只人类\N{\rENG}Oh! Looks like we got one of the humans anyway.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:03.66,0:01:05.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只有一个人类, 该怎么办呢\N{\rENG}Don't know what we'll do with just one of them,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:05.89,0:01:08.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还是交给钻石们去决定吧\N{\rENG}but I guess that's for the Diamonds to decide.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等, 海蓝宝, 咱们的协议就此终止! \N{\rENG}Wait. - Aquamarine, the deal is off.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.57,0:01:13.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你只能带走我一个\N{\rENG}You were only supposed to take me.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.57,0:01:14.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不带任何人类\N{\rENG}No humans.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他是人类\N{\rENG}That's a human.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.01,0:01:19.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 不\N{\rENG}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.27,0:01:23.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}小玫瑰因为她的小算盘没得意而生气了? \N{\rENG}Is Rosie upset 'cause her widdle "deal" didn't work?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.15,0:01:26.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}瞧, 我好悲伤, 我都哭了\N{\rENG}Look. I'm so moved, I'm crying.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.32,0:01:29.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}开玩笑的啦\N{\rENG}Just kidding.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.64,0:01:31.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是我的宝石\N{\rENG}That's my gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石, 你怎么看? \N{\rENG}Topaz, what do you think?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们该不该放她的朋友走呢? \N{\rENG}Should we let her friend go?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.59,0:01:38.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我同意\N{\rENG}I agree.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}去吧, 干活吧\N{\rENG}Go on. Do your thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦不不不不不不要再这样了\N{\rENG}Oh, no, no, no, no. Not again.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.97,0:01:52.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会向钻石们报告这位新囚犯的\N{\rENG}I'll go let the Diamonds know about our little prisoner.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来说说, 玫瑰, 我看上去怎么样? \N{\rENG}Say, Rose, how do I look?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.04,0:01:56.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}糟糕, 矮小, 还刻薄! \N{\rENG}Awful, small, and mean!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.88,0:02:01.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是你如何骗取那么多石的信任\N{\rENG}Is that how you flattered so many Gems
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.45,0:02:03.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}加入你的叛军联盟的吗? \N{\rENG}into joining your rebellion?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可爱死了\N{\rENG}How cute.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石, 我认为你还能自如操作飞船\N{\rENG}Topaz, I trust you'll still be able to fly the ship
Dialogue: 100,0:02:07.89,0:02:12.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尽管你…哎你懂的…身上多了点东西? \N{\rENG}despite your... you know....additions?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文, 这都是你的错\N{\rENG}Steven, this is all your fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这些奇怪的外星人之类的 都是因为你, 对不对? \N{\rENG}All this weird alien stuff -- this is 'cause of you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.14,0:02:26.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是的, 当然了! \N{\rENG}Yes, of course it is!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这也是为什么我用我自己 交换你们的安全! \N{\rENG}That's why I turned myself in -- to save all of you!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈, 可它进行的没那么顺利是不是? \N{\rENG}Well, it didn't really work out too well, did it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.31,0:02:35.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}除你以外所有人都安全下船了\N{\rENG}Well, everyone else managed to get off the ship.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以, 你当时在哪? \N{\rENG}So, where were you?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.48,0:02:38.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我狂跑, 然后藏起来了, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}I ran and hid, Steven,
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.49,0:02:41.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像任何有理智的人会…做\N{\rENG}like any sensible person would...do
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果他想被困在一艘飞船上\N{\rENG}if they wanted to get trapped on a ship.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.33,0:02:45.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Lars.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}莎蒂陷入了危险, 可我什么都没做\N{\rENG}Sadie was in trouble, and I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.26,0:02:51.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}事实上, 等等, 我还是有所作为的\N{\rENG}Actually, wait. I did do something.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我逃命, 我躲了起来, 就像我一直以来做的\N{\rENG}I ran and hid just like I always do.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像我没有去参加聚餐\N{\rENG}Just like I ran from the potluck.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.17,0:03:00.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可你被绑架了\N{\rENG}But you were abducted.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.18,0:03:01.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不是你的错\N{\rENG}That's not your fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.38,0:03:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 我把蛋糕卷扔了 然后跑掉了\N{\rENG}No, I trashed my roll and ran away.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后我才被绑架的\N{\rENG}Then I was abducted.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 为什么我就不能好好和人分享食物?!\N{\rENG}Oh, why couldn't I just let people eat my food?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得尽快把你送出去\N{\rENG}We have to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.59,0:03:13.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就交给我吧\N{\rENG}Here, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿! 瞧! 你捉到玫瑰石英了! \N{\rENG}Hey! Look! You have Rose Quartz!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么还要留着他? 他一点用都没有! \N{\rENG}Why bother with him? He's worthless!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真是谢谢啊, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Thanks a lot, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.23,0:03:24.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 我是指…没太大用, 不是没一点用\N{\rENG}No! I meant like "worth less", not "worthless"
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}跟…跟我比的话\N{\rENG}like...relative to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我至少还是一个不错的坐垫\N{\rENG}At least I make a great seat cushion.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.97,0:03:32.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}舒服不, 你个大香蕉? \N{\rENG}You feeling cozy, you big banana?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.78,0:03:35.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不认为她能听见\N{\rENG}I don't think she's listening.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.91,0:03:39.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能听见我吗, 你这个--杰米怎么说的来着? \N{\rENG}Can you hear me, you -- What was it Jamie said?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你这危险的大黄衣? \N{\rENG}You dangerous yellow coat?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她当然听不见你, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}Of course - she can't hear you, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.92,0:03:46.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她戴着那对大耳麦呢\N{\rENG}She's got those big headphones on.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}起飞时那些水晶战士一定是\N{\rENG}Those Crystal Gems must have screwed up the engine
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}把发动机弄坏了\N{\rENG}during takeoff.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石, 去把它修好\N{\rENG}Topaz, go fix it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.67,0:04:06.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯, 找找能帮助咱们的东西\N{\rENG}Lars, look for something that can help us.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个分解器\N{\rENG}A destabilizer.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.12,0:04:16.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}太完美了! \N{\rENG}That's perfect!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个分什么? \N{\rENG}A destaba-what?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它是一种可以破坏宝石人物理形态的武器\N{\rENG}It's a weapon that disrupts a Gem's physical form.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}酷, 多谢解释\N{\rENG}Cool. Thanks for explaining.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我还不懂它啥意思\N{\rENG}I still don't know what that means.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听我讲, 我有一个计划\N{\rENG}Just hear me out. I have a plan.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我需要你的帮助\N{\rENG}I'm gonna need you to be my arms.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 好吧\N{\rENG}Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯, 把我的裤子脱下来\N{\rENG}Lars, pull my pants off.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?! \N{\rENG}What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.47,0:04:35.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}相信我! 我想帮你\N{\rENG}Trust me! I'm trying to save you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可如果我不想被救呢? \N{\rENG}What if I don't want to be saved?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.18,0:04:40.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我只想被困在这里在宇宙里漂泊呢\N{\rENG}What if I want to stay trapped here and fly around space,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且为什么要脱你裤子, 你个怪胎?! \N{\rENG}and why your pants, you weirdo?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}脱就是了! \N{\rENG}Just do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 好 脱过了\N{\rENG}Ugh. There. I did it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很好, 现在把其中一只裤腿系成一个套索\N{\rENG}Great. Now tie one of the legs into a lasso.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做不到, 裤子在地上\N{\rENG}I can't. They're on the floor.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.32,0:04:56.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它们为什么会在地上?! \N{\rENG}What are they doing on the floor?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.38,0:04:58.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道, 史蒂文, 我们为什么会在宇宙里? \N{\rENG}I don't know, Steven. What are we doing in space?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.14,0:05:02.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯, 捡起来, 然后把它们系成一个套索\N{\rENG}Lars, pick them up - and then tie them into a lasso.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 随你吧\N{\rENG}Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔, 成功啦\N{\rENG}Wow. It worked.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们到家喽\N{\rENG}We're back home.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.80,0:05:09.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好计划\N{\rENG}Great plan.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.02,0:05:14.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在套住分解器\N{\rENG}Now lasso the destabilizer.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我还是不知道那是什么东西\N{\rENG}I still don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那个, 那个棍子\N{\rENG}That. That thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.05,0:05:19.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}加把劲啊, 拉尔斯, 你能做到的\N{\rENG}Come on, Lars. You can do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 成\N{\rENG}Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}加油, 再试一次\N{\rENG}Come on. Just one more try.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.32,0:05:31.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不想再试一次了\N{\rENG}I don't want to try again.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯, 扔出套索! \N{\rENG}Lars, throw the lasso!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.00,0:05:35.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}知道了! \N{\rENG}Fine!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.58,0:05:39.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你到底怎么了, 拉尔斯?! \N{\rENG}What is your problem, Lars?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么要这么做?! \N{\rENG}Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么你觉得我能干成一件事?! \N{\rENG}Why do you think I'm capable of anything?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你觉得我能, 我能做到, 但我做不到! \N{\rENG}You think I can do - all this stuff, but I can't!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做不到, 因为…\N{\rENG}I can't because...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是一个软蛋, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}I'm a wuss, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很害怕\N{\rENG}I'm just afraid.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.52,0:05:59.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我一直都这么活在恐惧和无知当中\N{\rENG}I've always just been stupid and afraid.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.09,0:06:03.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不像你, 总是在帮助他人\N{\rENG}Not like you. You're always helping people.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.09,0:06:06.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你从不畏惧什么\N{\rENG}You're never afraid.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.08,0:06:08.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯…\N{\rENG}Lars...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.06,0:06:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我现在就感到很害怕\N{\rENG}I'm afraid right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为只要我交出我自己, 一切就会重归原样, 但是…\N{\rENG}I thought if I turned myself in, it'd fix everything, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不想这么做, 拉尔斯\N{\rENG}I don't want to do this, Lars.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以前去过宇宙, 可不是像这样去的\N{\rENG}I've been to space before, but not like this.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们要将我直接交给那些残暴的首领手中\N{\rENG}They're taking me straight to their terrible leaders
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们想毁掉地球, 也想毁掉我\N{\rENG}that want to destroy Earth and destroy me
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只是为了一些我从未做过的事\N{\rENG}for something I never even did.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.50,0:06:33.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想要救所有人, 可我连那都做不到\N{\rENG}I just wanted to save everyone, but I couldn't even do that
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为, 你瞧, 你还在这里\N{\rENG}because, look -- you're still here.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文\N{\rENG}Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.06,0:06:39.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起\N{\rENG}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道该如何将你救出去\N{\rENG}I don't know how I'm gonna get you out of this.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会想办法的\N{\rENG}We'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们距离到达目的地大概还有\N{\rENG}We've got like a billion light-years
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}几十亿光年的 不是吗?\N{\rENG}till we get there, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有史以来第一次, \N{\rENG}For the first time ever,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要向积极的一面看了? \N{\rENG}you're gonna look on the bright side?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你 你不需要骗自己的\N{\rENG}Y-You don't have to sugarcoat this,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.81,0:06:58.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得了吧 你从来没这样积极过的\N{\rENG}but come on, you never do that.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.31,0:07:01.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你一直都毫无保留地和我抱怨一切都是那么糟糕\N{\rENG}You're always real with me about how much everything sucks.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧, 你是对的\N{\rENG}Okay. You're right.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这真的真的糟透了, 史蒂文\N{\rENG}This is really, really messed up, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你知道还有什么更糟的吗? \N{\rENG}You know what's even more messed up?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尽管这让你陷入了大危机\N{\rENG}Even though you're in huge trouble
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且全部都是我的错…\N{\rENG}and it's all my fault...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我却很高兴有你陪着我\N{\rENG}I'm kind of glad you're here.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我…\N{\rENG}I...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不希望独自一个人面对这一切\N{\rENG}I don't want to be alone right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.57,0:07:23.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是不是糟透了? \N{\rENG}Isn't that awful?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙计, 到现在这一步\N{\rENG}Dude, at this point,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:26.61,0:07:28.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一切都糟透了\N{\rENG}everything is awful.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很乐意抱抱你, 但我的胳膊被困住了\N{\rENG}I'd give you a hug, but I can't use my arms.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.36,0:07:44.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可以试试用我的腿抱你, 但估计会挺恶心的\N{\rENG}I could try using my legs, but it might be weird.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.30,0:07:51.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这, 这太美好了\N{\rENG}That's so, so beautiful.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尽管一切都将终结\N{\rENG}Even in the clutches of certain doom,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.94,0:07:56.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们还是很高兴拥有彼此\N{\rENG}you're happy to have each other.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托 托帕石\N{\rENG}T-T-Topaz.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.97,0:08:02.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道托帕石该怎么做, 如果她没有托帕石的话\N{\rENG}I don't know what Topaz would do if she didn't have Topaz.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我一直都想要告诉我\N{\rENG}I've always wanted to tell me
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我对我有多大帮助\N{\rENG}how I'm helping me through this,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.15,0:08:09.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我与我之间永远都有人阻挡着! \N{\rENG}but there's always someone between us!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.92,0:08:14.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们总是将我们送往这些不幸的任务\N{\rENG}They're always sending me on these miserable missions.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我总是骗自己我喜欢这些任务\N{\rENG}I'm always pretending I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.13,0:08:20.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我必须要假装我很好\N{\rENG}I have to pretend I'm fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.09,0:08:25.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你们, 你们对彼此如此坦诚\N{\rENG}But you two --you're so honest and open...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么\N{\rENG}so
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想帮助你们\N{\rENG}I want to help you guys.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们需要什么? \N{\rENG}What do you need?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}下船的方法\N{\rENG}A way off this ship.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有我的裤子\N{\rENG}And my pants.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好, 你们可以用逃生舱\N{\rENG}All right. - You can use this escape pod.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会为你们设下地球的坐标\N{\rENG}I'll set the coordinates for Earth.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.44,0:08:43.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好了, 拉尔斯, 快跳进去这件事就完成了\N{\rENG}All right, Lars, just get in and let it do its thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 你在说什么呢! 你也会跟我一起走, 不是吗? \N{\rENG}Guh. What are you talking about? You're coming, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不能, 我已经交出我自己了\N{\rENG}I can't. I turned myself in.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我还是要走的\N{\rENG}I still got to go.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.18,0:08:52.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}总有人需要为我母亲做的事付出代价\N{\rENG}Someone's got to pay for what my mom did.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但你不是不想这么做吗? \N{\rENG}But you don't want to do this?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙计, 别管那么多了, 快走吧\N{\rENG}Dude, forget it. Let's just go.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我...\N{\rENG}I-
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.18,0:08:59.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石, 你还在下面磨蹭什么呢\N{\rENG}Topaz, what are you still doing down here,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.83,0:09:00.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你这大石块? \N{\rENG}you big boulder?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们已经快到母星了\N{\rENG}We're almost to Homeworld.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.82,0:09:10.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你…在…做…什么? \N{\rENG}What...are...you...doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等, 我能解释\N{\rENG}Look, I can explain.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 他们置心长谈\N{\rENG}Um, they had this whole heartfelt thing
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有彼此多么好, 你错过了\N{\rENG}about being there for each other, and you missed it.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.95,0:09:20.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}实在是太感人了\N{\rENG}It was so moving.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 等等! \N{\rENG}No! Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我什么都看不到, 咱们的逃跑计划呢? \N{\rENG}I can't see what's happening. Are we still escaping?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.13,0:09:33.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不存在的! 没人逃跑! \N{\rENG}No! Nobody's escaping!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}海蓝宝, 咱们好好沟通一下\N{\rENG}Aquamarine, let's talk about this.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.88,0:09:40.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对, 我我想你也不是真的想伤害我们\N{\rENG}Yeah, I-I bet you don't really want to hurt us.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你--你只是表现得很刻薄\N{\rENG}You -- You probably just act mean
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为内心深处恐惧自己的弱小\N{\rENG}because deep down you're afraid you're weak.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.35,0:09:47.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来吧, 尽情讲, 我们都在分享情感呢\N{\rENG}Go ahead. Let it out. We're all sharing right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石, 你只有一项工作\N{\rENG}Topaz, you had one job,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你不想做这份工作\N{\rENG}and if you're not gonna do it,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.92,0:09:56.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那你已经毫无用处了! \N{\rENG}you're of no use to me!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔哦! \N{\rENG}Ooh!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}叛乱…是吧? \N{\rENG}So...a revolt, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在此之后你又打算怎么做? \N{\rENG}And what do you plan to do after this?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.77,0:10:16.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}回到钻石身边? 拿着我的宝石? \N{\rENG}Go back to the Diamonds? My gem in your hand?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.24,0:10:18.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们肯定要高兴坏了\N{\rENG}I'm sure they'll love that.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而你们也会被重赏\N{\rENG}You'll be rewarded handsomely
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.22,0:10:24.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}被分离, 被粉碎\N{\rENG}by being separated and shattered.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在想什么呢! \N{\rENG}What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是你们这群融合体的毛病\N{\rENG}That's the problem with you fusions.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.48,0:10:39.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}迟早, 你们都变得感情用事\N{\rENG}Sooner or later, - you all become sentimental.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们到了\N{\rENG}We're here.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这样, 只要你们解除融合\N{\rENG}Look, just unfuse,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们就不再提起这件事了\N{\rENG}and we'll never speak of this again.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.89,0:11:00.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}托帕石, 你不必这么做\N{\rENG}Topaz, you don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.96,0:11:04.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等, 拉尔斯! \N{\rENG}Wait. Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文, 她们要把我们送到哪里?! \N{\rENG}Steven, where are they taking us?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.00,0:11:07.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道! \N{\rENG}I don't know!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! \N{\rENG}Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯! \N{\rENG}Lars!
